          "message": "fix(sqlite): drive all 782 SqliteFs tests green — fix 16 remaining failures\n\nFixes:\n- createPartition: lastInsertIno bug (dentry rowid vs inode ino)\n- writeFile: follow symlinks, update parent mtime on new file\n- readFile: trailing slash on file throws ENOTDIR\n- stat: empty path throws ENOENT\n- mkdir: root path throws EEXIST, recursive follows symlinks\n- exists: propagate ENAMETOOLONG\n- persistence test: set PRAGMA user_version after Schema.create\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
